div.p: This step checks if a user is already authenticated based on the provided cookie.
Sessions are handled by the CakePHP's Session Component. Validity of a session is ensured via the component's own logic and includes checks such as comparison against User Agent and Time.
If inconsistencies or tampering is detected. The session is destroyed and a new one is created.
